  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4458267">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4458267/" class="title-link">着实需细细品读</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4458267"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/19129723/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u19129723-13.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/19129723/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">三日月</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-11-10"
      class="main-meta">2010-11-10 19:29:18</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4458267_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         曹先生本人有着浓厚的国学根底，虽然本书瞩目于批判旧学，然言语中仍可窥探旧日国学特别是学术思想史之一斑。     另外，需要提示的是，阅读此书可能不同于其它随笔，本书的知识性极强，而且涉及国学各个门类，过往典故亦不在少数，实需花大力气去阅读，方能得之精髓。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
