  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5287732/" class="title-link">为什么不读古书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5287732"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sesinx/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1374575-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sesinx/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">小清25年</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-01-31"
      class="main-meta">2012-01-31 21:03:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5287732_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  曹老先生告诉我们，古书中的古意难寻，且说法各异，以年青人（个别天才除外）的学识根本读不出古书的原意，所以现在号召大家读古书的人，多是以读经典的名义贩卖私货。读懂古书，要花费大量的精力，以这样的精力，倒不如做些前沿科学知识。综上，曹老先生觉得年青人没必要读古...

